### 3. Firestore Security Rules â€” Not Configured

> [!CAUTION]
> No `firestore.rules` file was found in the project. The PDF spec requires:
> - Only authenticated users can access tenant portal
> - Only admin can access admin panel
> - Tenants can only see their own bills
> - Tenants can see all complaints for their property

**Current state:** Client-side route protection exists (`ProtectedRoute` component), but no server-side Firestore security rules are in place. This is a **security vulnerability** â€” anyone could read/write directly to the database.

